net.proteusframework.cms.component.editor

Interface DelegatePurpose

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DropOption, LocalizedNamedObject, NamedObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDelegatePurpose

    public interface DelegatePurpose
extends LocalizedNamedObject, DropOption
    Identifies the purpose of the delegating data.

    For persistence, implementations should provide a static valueOf(String) method that returns an instance based on the name.

    Author:
    Ben Barber (bbarber@i2rd.com)
